   Any other duties commensurate with the job role.
   The ideal candidate should have;
    Understanding and compliance of Health & Safety Regulations
    Previous Crane driving experience
    Ability to work individually and also as part of a team
    Ability to use own initiative and be self-motivated
    Flexible, modern attitude to work and manufacturing processes
    Willing to work on a shift basis
    Experience of operating a Counter balance Fork Lift Truck as well as
   Cherry Picker and Scissor Lift access equipment
    Previous experience in a heavy engineering environment
